    <p>
     The fold of the SSD is unprecedented. Structural homologues (
     <em>
      Z
     </em>
     -score &lt;3.6) identified by the Dali server show limited similarity only to helices α8–α12 of the SSD structure (
     <xref ref-type="bibr">
      Holm and Sander, 1993
     </xref>
