   <sec>
    <title>
     Crystal structure of the Shq1-specific domain in complex with Cbf5, Nop10 and Gar1
    </title>
    <p>
     To reveal the molecular detail of the Shq1–Cbf5 interaction, we determined the crystal structure of the SSD in complex with Cbf5, Nop10 and Gar1 at 3.06 Å resolution. The structure was solved by molecular replacement and refined to an
     <em>
